node.text: The bag has spoken again, this time its me vs dave. Ive had the pleasure of racing the fastest guys every week, and this week is no different! After the last two racenights, dave is undefeated sitting at 4 and 0. Tbh there aint but 1 or 2 guys out here that can stop dave from going undefeated...and im one of them! If im going to earn my spot on Americas List, this is how i do it. If i aint undefeated, then nobody is going undefeated if i can help it lol. What lane you got? #streetoutlaws #405 #americaslist #handingoutLs #travelingLsalesman #bigchief #freeLdeliveries #wefinanceLs #90dayssameascash #nowarranties #gonnasuckifilose #humblelol #481xLOL

node.text: Illegal testing on the street, is the best way to see how much this shit means to people. And you can tell we got the right group of guys here in the 405! Just when you start to think these guys are going soft, raise the stakes and watch us rise to the challenge! Even the new guy Damon was out beating up the streets, and that makes me proud. Pick the 5 guys you think will win it all!!! i know the 5 i would pick, who you riding with?? @lutzracecars @jackiebraaasch #streetoutlaws #bestreet #or #beaint #americaslist #405iscoming #andhelliscomingwithme #streetracer #405 #lesssgetttittt💪

node.text: Dont miss the new episode of Street Outlaws OG at 7, followed by new episode of Mega Cash Days all on @discovery tonight!!! When it comes to the list, or no prep racing ive proven dozens of times that daddy dave cant outrun me, but during cash days competition i dont think ive ever been able to get to the stripe before dave. JJDaBoss was on the starting line with dave discussing the complexity of the situation, and as you can see here JJ was covering all bets and maybe he knew something everyone else didnt??
